      Parameters:
      allele_id - the id of the allele in variant_summary.txt

      pathogenicity - the pathogenicity in variant_summary.txt
      gene_id - the id of the gene in variant_summary.txt
      rs - the rs id in variant_summary.txt
      type - the type in variant_summary.txt
      alternate_allele - the alternate allele in variant_summary.txt
      disease - the disease code in variant_summary.txt
      reference_allele - the reference allele in variant_summary.txt
      chromosome - the chromosome in variant_summary.txt
